long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: UMass Professor Ratings is a tool that helps students of UMass Amherst select their courses and professors. With this extension installed, ratings for each professor are displayed next to the professor's name, as well as a link to every in depth review.
